QuestData.Title: Da Perfect Spies
QuestData.Description: Now, it would be foolish to go in blind 'ere, so I be creatin' some tiny spies to gather information for Vol'jin. He got to know what's goin' on over on de islands.$B$BI could use da help, if you be feelin' up to it. I tell ya how it's done. First, ya gotta catch de frogs. Dey like to stay in de shade of da palm trees around Sen'jin.$B$BOnce ya have de frogs, bring 'em over here to my sentry totem an' attune dem to me sight.
QuestData.LogDescription: Capture 5 Sen'jin Frogs and attune them to Vanira's sight at her Sentry Totem.
QuestData.RewardText: These be enough for me purposes. Now comes de hard part.
